## Summary
This documentation explains how to create custom SQL queries with Amplitude Query, a product add-on that allows users to search raw data through a Snowflake database. It details the Query schema, table naming conventions, column descriptions, and how to use the Amplitude SQL chart type to visualize query results within the Amplitude platform.

